<font size="2" style="font-size: 9pt;">Strong computer literacy. Must be internet savvy.</font></p>
</li>
<li>
<p align="JUSTIFY" style="margin-bottom: 0in;">
<font size="2" style="font-size: 9pt;">Ability to learn new tasks quickly.</font></p>
