<p align="JUSTIFY" style="margin-bottom: 0in;">
<br />
This full-time position will pay $12.00 an hour for an 8.5 hour shift, which will include a half hour unpaid lunch break. Our ideal candidate will be flexible with their hours of availability, as the Dept requires coverage from 9 AM to 9 PM Monday through Friday. *Prior event ticketing experience a plus, but not required.&nbsp;</p>
