	What will I be doing?</h2>
<p>
	We try to structure our internships around the interests of the intern. &nbsp;We see our internships as an educational experience where new developers can be exposed to things the classroom left out. &nbsp;Previous internships have included working with AWS S3 for managing user media assets, Redis&nbsp;in-memory key-val&nbsp;DB for replacing disk based sessions, working with Scribe for distributed log management and more. &nbsp;No matter what your projects are here, you&#39;ll be exposed what agile software development is like in the real world.</p>
