</ul>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
3+ years of B2B outside sales experience is required, along&nbsp;with a track record of consistently achieving aggressive sales targets.</li>
<li>
Experience working for a software company and/or in the event ticketing industry.</li>
<li>
<strong>MUST be self-motivated</strong>, outgoing and well-organized while managing several prospects at the same time.</li>
<li>
Eager to sell! Ability to sell to and negotiate with prospects at all decision-making levels.</li>
<li>
Should possess sound business judgment, recognizing the balance between achieving sales targets and maintaining or increasing pricing.</li>
<li>
Ability to travel frequently.</li>
