			<description><![CDATA[<p>
ShowClix, a fast-growing, Pittsburgh-based event ticketing company, is actively seeking an innovative, results-oriented Lead Generation Specialist to create, uncover, qualify, and develop potential sales opportunities to be passed to the sales team, while promoting a synergistic environment between sales and marketing. This is mainly a communications position that performs prospecting functions that support the company&rsquo;s sales team. The ideal candidate will utilize their professional communication, solid research abilities, as well as marketing and sales skills.</p>
<p>
Perks include a competitive salary, benefits package, and a truly awesome office environment. To learn more about life at ShowClix, visit http://www.showclix.com/about/culture.</p>
<br />
<p>
Key Responsibilities</p>
<p>
<br />
- Execute prompt follow-up on inbound leads generated through marketing efforts.</p>
<p>
- Meet and exceed monthly lead generation goals, which include completing a high volume of outbound calls each day (between 80 &ndash; 100) to companies and organizations seeking a full-service event ticketing solution and securing 80 demos per month for the sales team.</p>
<p>
- Communicate with prospects to determine their purchase decision criteria, budgets, timelines, decision-making process, purchasing process, the decision-makers, and key influencers.</p>
<p>
- Develop and maintain customer profiles across multiple verticals, as well as an effective outbound calling strategy, and call and email scripts.</p>
<p>
- Monitor and analyze performance against lead and pipeline goals and continually make and implement recommendations for optimization and ongoing growth.</p>
<br />
<p>
Qualifications</p>
<p>
- Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree.</p>
<p>
- Must be a self- starter with a proven track record of excellent communicative/strategic selling skills.</p>
<p>
- Superior oral and written interpersonal communication skills, and able to communicate well with both technical and non-technical individuals.</p>
<p>
- Must have outbound business-to-business phone marketing or sales experience.</p>
<p>
- CRM experience preferred.</p>
<p>
- Tenacious and willing to place hundreds of calls per week.</p>
<p>
- Ability to navigate corporate structures to identify decision makers and determine buying process.</p>
<p>
- Ability to be assertive and persuasive without being aggressive.</p>
<p>
- Active listening skills.</p>
<p>
- Self-motivated with an entrepreneurial spirit.</p>
<p>
<br />
About ShowClix: ShowClix is a full-service, primary ticketing company that provides venues, promoters and event organizers with innovative solutions to manage every aspect of their ticketing operations, including online and telephone ticket sales, box office management, admissions control, and event promotion. The company currently works with over 5,000 live music venues, performing arts groups, museums, festivals, nightclubs, artist management companies, non-profit organizations and colleges and universities around the world.<br />
&nbsp;</p>
